description:
What do the Bible and Spirit of Prophecy say about the role of the pastor in the local church? This is one topic of discussion in this week’s episode of #ANNProfiles with Alyssa Truman. Listen to the story of Gerson Santos, associate secretary of the General Conference of Seventh-day Adventists, on how he came to know Jesus, his experience as a pastor, and now as a World Church leader. 

For the full episode, copy and paste this link into your browser: 
https://youtu.be/uWNh_TzCE6M
